OOP Online Judge — Work Schema (May 2026)

Member 1 (Your Work)
--------------------
Goal: Design and implement Authentication + User UI flow (console UI).

1) Login Screen
   - Features:
     - Login by username + password
     - Show specific error messages (wrong password / user not found / not verified)
     - Input cannot be skipped by pressing Enter (required input)
   - Main files used:
     - OOP-Online-Judge/src/LoginScreen.cpp
     - OOP-Online-Judge/include/LoginScreen.h
     - OOP-Online-Judge/include/UserManager.h
     - OOP-Online-Judge/src/UserManager.cpp

2) Signup / Register Screen
   - Features:
     - Register username + email + password
     - Email validation: must end with "@email.com"
     - Duplicate username check: show "User already exists"
     - Verification token shown after register
     - Token entry step cannot be skipped by Enter (type "SKIP" to skip)
   - Main files used:
     - OOP-Online-Judge/src/RegisterScreen.cpp
     - OOP-Online-Judge/include/RegisterScreen.h
     - OOP-Online-Judge/include/UserManager.h
     - OOP-Online-Judge/src/UserManager.cpp
     - OOP-Online-Judge/include/VerificationService.h
     - OOP-Online-Judge/src/VerificationService.cpp

3) User Panel (Dashboard) + Options
   - Features:
     - After login, show user panel/dashboard
     - Options: Browse Problems, Start Contest, Resume Contest, View Last Result
     - Options: Logout, Delete Account, Exit
     - Input cannot be skipped by pressing Enter
   - Main files used:
     - OOP-Online-Judge/src/DashboardScreen.cpp
     - OOP-Online-Judge/include/DashboardScreen.h
     - OOP-Online-Judge/src/UIManager.cpp
     - OOP-Online-Judge/include/UIManager.h
     - OOP-Online-Judge/include/UserManager.h
     - OOP-Online-Judge/src/UserManager.cpp

4) UI Flow / Navigation (overall console UI)
   - Features:
     - Main menu (Login / Register / Exit)
     - After login: route to Dashboard actions
     - Consistent, required input prompts (no Enter skipping)
   - Main files used:
     - OOP-Online-Judge/main.cpp
     - OOP-Online-Judge/src/UIManager.cpp

